  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In the present study, the effects of 5 days of lower limb immobilization with or without
      daily neuromuscular electrical stimulation on muscle mass and muscle fiber characteristics
      will be determined.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
